title: Update: She Accidently Catfished Him And IS Scared To Tell The Truth!
description:
I think we all can agree that catfishing is just disrespectful. Someone creates a fake social media account to pretend to be someone else in hopes of beginning a deceitful relationship; doesn’t that just sound downright evil?
But what if someone does it by accident, does it count? And what if they’re ready to come clean about the whole thing and see where destiny takes them, should the catfishee go out with them anyway?!
